links.title: Marvell Confirms Merger With Chipmaker Inphi To Create $40B Entity
links.description: Marvell Technology Group Ltd (NASDAQ: MRVL) on Thursday confirmed its acquisition of semiconductor manufacturer Inphi Corporation (NASDAQ: IPHI). What Happened: The two companies will create a combined entity - with a $40 billion enterprise valuation - where Marvell will hold a majority stake with 83% and Inphi will control the balance 17% of the newly-created company.
